Welcome

 









Member 
        SIPC/FINRA


 

















































































P.R. Herzig & Co., Inc., 
                        managed since 1957 by its founding family, is 
                        a registered investment adviser and licensed 
                        broker-dealer that provides quality, independent 
                        investment advice and portfolio management to a loyal 
                        clientele of wealthy individuals, pension funds, 
                        trusts, charitable foundations and funds of funds seeking personalized 
                        and responsive service less readily available from larger financial 
                        institutions.
We are iconoclastic, value-driven, and independent 
                          thinkers; we do not chase market trends or 
                          popular investment "styles."
 
We invest our money alongside that of our clients; 
                          when our clients do well, we do well.
 
We value integrity; 
							we place the interest of our clients above our own.
 
MOVING NOTICE
On July 7, 2016 we relocated to new offices in the same 
						complex. Our new address is:
 4 Expressway Plaza Suite 220
Roslyn Heights, NY 11577
Our telephone and fax numbers remain the same.
 

