Performance











		  














         
 
 




Performance

 









Member 
        SIPC/FINRA


 

















































































We consider ourselves investment 
                        professionals rather than asset gatherers. We do not try 
                        to grow our business by selling investment "products."
                        
Instead, we focus on obtaining the 
                        best investment results we can for our clients, 
                        consistent with their individual needs and 
                        circumstances.
To measure our progress, we have tracked the 
						"time-weighted" 
                        net of fees performance of 
                        individually managed accounts since the mid 1980s, long before it 
                        was common to do so. 
Clients are encouraged to discuss with 
						us the long-term performance of their accounts. 
Past performance, of course, does not 
                        guarantee future results.
 
 
 
 
 
 

 
