Roslyn Heights, NY, based Investment company P.R. Herzig & Co. Inc. buys Hanesbrands Inc, SPDR Series Trust S&P Biotech, Hexcel Corp, Spectra Energy Partners LP, United States Steel Corp, PayPal Holdings Inc, McDonald's Corp, Starbucks Corp, sells PTC Inc, Mohawk Industries Inc, Schlumberger, O'Reilly Automotive Inc, Mednax Inc during the 3-months ended 2017-06-30, according to the most recent filings of the investment company, P.R. Herzig & Co. Inc.. As of 2017-06-30, P.R. Herzig & Co. Inc. owns 50 stocks with a total value of $52 million.  These are the details of the buys and sells.New Purchases: HBI, XBI, HXL, SEP, X, MCD, SBUX, Added Positions: PYPL, IBM, BMY, NEM, SENEA, MCK, Reduced Positions: ORLY, GE, AAPL, COH, GOOG, SJT, DIS, MSFT, FNF, FB, Sold Out: PTC, MHK, SLB, MD, 
